            "tag": "Summer Exclusive",
            "heading": "Balancing Floral",
            "details": "Inspired by summer’s most tranquil gardens, our Balancing Floral is a rich combination of lemon peel, rose geranium, and earthy vetiver. Peppered with antibacterial properties, this blend is both calming and incredibly effective."
          }
